o\">\n    <big>\n\n\n\n教师详细信息</big><div class=\"fr\">当前位置：\n                        <a href=\"../../index.htm\">首页</a>\n                <i>&gt;</i>\n                <a href=\"../../yjry/jy.htm\">研究人员</a>\n                <i>&gt;</i>\n                <a href=\"../../yjry/jsxxxx.htm\">教师详细信息</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<section class=\"n_container\">\n    <section class=\"n_left fl\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n        <section class=\"n_news_detail\">\n\n\n\n\n<script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/interface/NewsvoteDWR.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"../../_dwr/engine.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/news/newscontent.js\"></script><link href=\"/system/resource/js/photoswipe/3.0.5.1/photoswipe.css\" type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/photoswipe/3.0.5.1/klass.min.js\"></script><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n<div class=\"ar_article_box\">\n    <div class=\"nav01\">\n        <h3>汪   忠</h3>\n        <h6>\n            <span>日期：<font>2020-12-21</font></span>\n            <span>浏览量：<font><script>_showDynClicks(\"wbnews\", 1703716603, 1216)</script><span id=\"dynclicks_wbnews_1216_161\" name=\"dynclicks_wbnews_1216_161\">16855</span></font></span>\n        </h6>\n    </div>\n    <div id=\"vsb_content\" class=\"ar_article\"><div class=\"v_news_content\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;\">\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_img\" style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 0px;\"><img src=\"/__local/7/8A/7E/A0CC92B645FAFAD4054BB9C7921_0B31AE42_6AD1.jpg\" width=\"208\" height=\"255\" border=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" title=\"6AD1\" alt=\"6AD1\" vsbhref=\"vurl\" vurl=\"/_vsl/78A7EA0CC92B645FAFAD4054BB9C7921/0B31AE42/6AD1\" vheight=\" 255px\" vwidth=\" 208px\" orisrc=\"/__local/7/8A/7E/A0CC92B645FAFAD4054BB9C7921_0B31AE42_6AD1.jpg\" class=\"img_vsb_content\" style=\"width: 208px; height: 255px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_img\" style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 0px;\"><strong>汪忠 </strong>教授</p>\n<p>电子邮箱：wangzhongemail(at)tsinghua.edu.cn</p>\n<h4><p>教育背景</p></h4>\n<p>2011 博士学位 中国科学技术大学 近代物理系</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 2em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;导师：完绍龙教授, 张首晟教授</p>\n<p>10/2009-09/2010 斯坦福大学</p>\n<p>2005 学士学位 中国科学技术大学</p>\n<h4 style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p>工作履历</p></h4>\n<p>08/2022 - 至今&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 清华大学高等研究院 教授</p>\n<p>12/2015 - 07/2022&nbsp; &nbsp;清华大学高等研究院 研究员</p>\n<p>03/2011 - 11/2015&nbsp; &nbsp;清华大学高等研究院 副研究员</p>\n<h4 style=\"white-space: normal;\"><p>研究领域</p></h4>\n<p>主要研究领域为凝聚态物理，同时关注若干交叉方向。目前主要研究方向为:</p>\n<p>1. 拓扑物态与拓扑现象</p>\n<p>2. 关联量子物态</p>\n<p>3. 非厄米物理</p>\n<h4><p>学术成果</p></h4>\n<p>发表论文:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://publons.com/researcher/2221010/zhong-wang/publications/\" target=\"_self\" textvalue=\"ResearcherID\">ResearcherID</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?hl=en&amp;user=ekjj9m4AAAAJ\" target=\"_self\" textvalue=\"Google Scholar\">Google Scholar</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/a/wang_z_10\" target=\"_self\" textvalue=\"arXiv\">arXiv</a></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>代表性论文:</p>\n<p>22. Non-Hermitian edge burst</p>\n<p>Wen-Tan Xue, Yu-Min Hu, Fei Song, <strong>Zhong Wang</strong></p>\n<p>Phys. Rev. Lett. 128, 120401 (2022)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>21. Observation of Non-Bloch Parity-Time Symmetry and Exceptional Points</p>\n<p>Lei Xiao, Tianshu Deng, Kunkun Wang, <strong>Zhong Wang</strong>, Wei Yi, Peng Xue</p>\n<p>Phys. Rev. Lett. 126, 230402 (2021)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>20. Solving the Liouvillian Gap with Artificial Neural Networks</p>\n<p>Dong Yuan, He-Ran Wang, <strong>Zhong Wang</strong>, Dong-Ling Deng</p>\n<p>Phys. Rev. Lett. 126, 160401 (2021)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>19. Simple formulas of directional amplification from non-Bloch band theory</p>\n<p>Wen-Tan Xue, Ming-Rui Li, Yu-Min Hu, Fei Song, <strong>Zhong Wang</strong></p>\n<p>Phys. Rev. B 103, L241408 (2021)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>18. Non-Hermitian bulk-boundary correspondence in quantum dynamics</p>\n<p>Lei Xiao, Tianshu Deng, Kunkun Wang, Gaoyan Zhu, <strong>Zhong Wang</strong>, Wei Yi, Peng Xue</p>\n<p>Nat. Phys. 16, 761 (2020)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>17. Dirac-vortex topological cavities</p>\n<p>Xiaomei Gao, Lechen Yang, Hao Lin, Lang Zhang, Jiafang Li, Fang Bo, <strong>Zhong Wang</strong>, Ling Lu</p>\n<p>Nature Nanotechnology, 15, 1012 (2020)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>16. Non-Hermitian skin effect and chiral damping in open quantum systems</p>\n<p>Fei Song, Shunyu Yao, <strong>Zhong Wang</strong></p>\n<p>Phys. Rev. Lett. 123, 170401 (2019)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>15. Non-Hermitian Topological Invariants in Real Space</p>\n<p>Fei Song, Shunyu Yao, <strong>Zhong Wang</strong></p>\n<p>Phys. Rev. Lett. 123, 246801 (2019)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>14. Majorana corner modes in a high-temperature platform</p>\n<p>Zhongbo Yan, Fei Song, <strong>Zhong Wang</strong></p>\n<p>Phys. Rev. Lett. 121, 096803 (2018)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>13. Non-Hermitian Chern bands</p>\n<p>Shunyu Yao, Fei Song, <strong>Zhong Wang</strong></p>\n<p>Phys. Rev. Lett. 121, 136802 (2018)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>12. Edge states and topological invariants of non-Hermitian systems</p>\n<p>Shunyu Yao, <strong>Zhong Wang</strong></p>\n<p>Phys. Rev. Lett. 121, 086803 (2018)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>11. Experimental discovery of nodal chains</p>\n<p>Qinghui Yan, Rongjuan Liu, Zhongbo Yan, Boyuan Liu, Hongsheng Chen, <strong>Zhong Wang</strong>, Ling Lu</p>\n<p>Nature Physics 14, 461 (2018)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>10. Majorana Zero Modes Protected by Hopf Invariant in Topologically Trivial Superconductors</p>\n<p>Zhongbo Yan, Ren Bi, <strong>Zhong Wang</strong></p>\n<p>Phys. Rev. Lett. 118, 147003 (2017)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>9. Topological invariants of Floquet systems: General formulation, special properties, and Floquet topological defects</p>\n<p>Shunyu Yao, Zhongbo Yan, <strong>Zhong Wang</strong></p>\n<p>Phys. Rev. B 96, 195303 (2017)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>8. Nodal-link semimetals</p>\n<p>Zhongbo Yan, Ren Bi, Huitao Shen, Ling Lu, Shou-Cheng Zhang, <strong>Zhong Wang</strong></p>\n<p>Phys. Rev. B 96, 041103(R) (2017)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>7. Tunable Weyl Semimetals in Periodically Driven Nodal Line Semimetals</p>\n<p>Zhongbo Yan, <strong>Zhong Wang</strong></p>\n<p>Phys. Rev. Lett. 117, 087402 (2016)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>6. Helical Spin Order from Topological Dirac and Weyl Semimetals</p>\n<p>Xiao-Qi Sun, Shou-Cheng Zhang, <strong>Zhong Wang</strong></p>\n<p>Phys. Rev. Lett. 115, 076802 (2015)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>5. Topological Invariants and Ground States Wavefunctions of Topological Insulators on a Torus</p>\n<p><strong>Zhong Wang</strong>, Shou-Cheng Zhang</p>\n<p>Phys. Rev. X 4, 011006 (2014)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>4. Chiral anomaly, charge density waves, and axion strings from Weyl semimetals</p>\n<p><strong>Zhong Wang</strong>, Shou-Cheng Zhang</p>\n<p>Phys. Rev. B 87, 161107(R) (2013)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>3. Simplified Topological Invariants for Interacting Insulators</p>\n<p><strong>Zhong Wang</strong> and Shou-Cheng Zhang</p>\n<p>Phys. Rev. X 2, 031008 (2012)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>2. Topological order parameters for interacting topological insulators</p>\n<p><strong>Zhong Wang</strong>, Xiao-Liang Qi, Shou-Cheng Zhang</p>\n<p>Phys. Rev. Lett. 105, 256803(2010)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>1. Equivalent topological invariants of topological insulators</p>\n<p><strong>Zhong Wang</strong>, Xiao-Liang Qi and Shou-Cheng Zhang</p>\n<p>New J. Phys. 12, 065007 (2010)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n</div></div><div id=\"div_vote_id\"></div>\n        \n        <section id=\"ar_fot\">\n            <h1 class=\"highlight prev\"><a href=\"1218.htm\"><span>上一篇：</span>Manuel Valiente</a></h1>\n            <h1 class=\"highlight next\"><a href=\"1215.htm\"><span>下一篇：</span>姚   宏</a></h1>\n            <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n        </section>\n   \n    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div>\n</form>\n</section>\n        